Package org.framed.orm.ui.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FulfillRolesCommand
    This command is used from the FulfillRolesAction and the RolesDialog to add all of the choosen Shapes from type roletype and rolegroups to the fulfilledRoles list of a Relation from type fulfillment and delete of the not choosen rolegroups and roleTypes from the referencedRoles list of a fulfillment.
    ORMAddCommand  
    ORMCloneCommand  
    ORMNamedElementRenameCommand
    Through this command the name of a NamedElement can be changed.
    ORMOrphanChildCommand  
    StepCommand
    This command realize the step in/out, which is initialized by the StepInAction, the StepInNewPageAction, the StepInNewTabAction or the StepOutAction, through changing the content of the viewer of the ORMMultiPageEditor instance, which owns the Shape from type compartmentype or group the user wants to step in/out.
